Indonesian-speaking Counsel, Security services
– 3+ years PQE
Location:  Singapore
Our client is a company which looks after the welfare and health of international travellers. There is now a vacancy for a legal counsel to join their dynamic global legal team. The successful candidate will be based in Singapore and enjoy a full range of responsibilities providing legal support for our client's business operations in Indonesia and South East Asia.
The ideal candidate should have at least 3 years of good Indonesia-related corporate and commercial experience gained in a leading firm or in-house with a MNC. Complete fluency in Bahasa Indonesia is a must.
